00:00:55.160 --> 00:00:57.700
A two and a half year old
startup that helps unmarried

00:00:57.700 --> 00:01:00.630
couples in India book
hotel rooms discretely.

00:01:00.630 --> 00:01:03.530
The founders felt compelled to
create Stay Uncle after hearing

00:01:03.530 --> 00:01:06.180
story after story of
young unmarried couples

00:01:06.180 --> 00:01:09.519
trying and failing to conduct
relationships in secret.

