00:01:11.060 --> 00:01:14.730
we saw those almost horror
stories which our couples were

00:01:14.730 --> 00:01:15.520
sharing with us.

00:01:15.520 --> 00:01:18.360
How they were denied
hotel stays at 2 o'clock.

00:01:18.360 --> 00:01:21.246
