00:01:33.400 --> 00:01:35.750
NARRATOR: The service
set-up is simple.

00:01:35.750 --> 00:01:37.900
Couples can log on to
Stay Uncle's website

00:01:37.900 --> 00:01:40.210
to find an array of hotels
that will accept them

00:01:40.210 --> 00:01:42.430
with no issue,
which is technically

00:01:42.430 --> 00:01:46.340
the law for all hotels as
long as the guests are of age.

00:01:46.340 --> 00:01:48.270
But most importantly
couples who book

00:01:48.270 --> 00:01:50.364
a hotel through the
website are assured

00:01:50.364 --> 00:01:51.780
that they will be
safe from attack

00:01:51.780 --> 00:01:55.072
at the hotel they
choose to stay in.

00:01:55.072 --> 00:01:56.530
SANCHIT SETHI: We
