00:02:08.325 --> 00:02:09.699
NARRATOR: However,
Stay Uncle was

00:02:09.699 --> 00:02:11.448
difficult to get off
the ground initially.

00:02:15.517 --> 00:02:17.850
SANCHIT SETHI: It has been
pretty difficult because what

00:02:17.850 --> 00:02:20.780
we're trying to do is something
the industry's not used to,

00:02:20.780 --> 00:02:23.480
and the people aren't used to,
not even the customers, not

00:02:23.480 --> 00:02:25.200
the suppliers.

00:02:25.200 --> 00:02:29.010
NARRATOR: Eventually some hotels
